title: Essential Doctor Strange, Vol. 3
description: After earning the title of Sorcerer Supreme, Doctor Strange must defend his title, his life and his world against enemies old and new! Dormammu, Silver Dagger, Nightmare, Stygyro and more test Strange's sorcery and sanity!Collects: DOCTOR STRANGE #1-29 and ANNUAL #1, and TOMB OF DRACULA #44-45.
author: Steve Englehart
